Sum of elements in array:

Link: http://geeksforgeeks.org/problems/sum-of-array2326/1

Java Implementation:

// User function Template for Java

class Solution {
    int arraySum(int arr[]) {
        // code here
        int sum=0;
        for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++){
            sum=sum+arr[i];
        }
        return sum;
    }
}
